// ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄
// TEXT SELECTION BEHAVIORS
// ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄

        // Select all macro
        #define select_all kp _C(A)

        // Select word (with direction based on shift)
        select_word_right: select_word_right {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-macro";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            wait-ms = <10>;
            tap-ms = <10>;
            bindings = <&kp LC(RIGHT) &kp LS(LC(RIGHT))>;
        };
        select_word_left: select_word_left {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-macro";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            wait-ms = <10>;
            tap-ms = <10>;
            bindings = <&kp LC(LEFT) &kp LS(LC(LEFT))>;
        };
        select_word: select_word {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-mod-morph";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            bindings = <&select_word_right>, <&select_word_left>;
            mods = <(MOD_LSFT|MOD_RSFT)>;
        };

        // Extend word (extend selection by one word)
        extend_word_right: extend_word_right {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-macro";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            wait-ms = <10>;
            tap-ms = <10>;
            bindings = <&kp LS(LC(RIGHT))>;
        };
        extend_word_left: extend_word_left {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-macro";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            wait-ms = <10>;
            tap-ms = <10>;
            bindings = <&kp LS(LC(LEFT))>;
        };
        extend_word: extend_word {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-mod-morph";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            bindings = <&extend_word_right>, <&extend_word_left>;
            mods = <(MOD_LSFT|MOD_RSFT)>;
        };

        // Parenthesis/angle bracket morphs
        parang_left: parang_left {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-mod-morph";
            label = "PARANG_LEFT";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            bindings = <&kp LPAR>, <&kp LT>;
            mods = <(MOD_LSFT|MOD_RSFT)>;
        };
        parang_right: parang_right {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-mod-morph";
            label = "PARANG_RIGHT";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            bindings = <&kp RPAR>, <&kp GT>;
            mods = <(MOD_LSFT|MOD_RSFT)>;
        };

        // Euro symbol macro (Windows: Alt+0128)
        euro_symbol: euro_symbol {
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-macro";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            wait-ms = <10>;
            tap-ms = <10>;
            bindings = <&macro_press &kp LALT>
                     , <&macro_tap &kp KP_N0 &kp KP_N1 &kp KP_N2 &kp KP_N8>
                     , <&macro_release &kp LALT>;
        };

